*libgaminggear-0.4.0 (06 Sep 2014)

  06 Sep 2014; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org>
  +libgaminggear-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Version bump. Bug #520284

  24 Jul 2014; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  libgaminggear-0.2.0.ebuild, libgaminggear-0.3.0.ebuild:
  Remove virtual/udev dependency from 0.3.0 because libgaminggear-0.3.0.tar.bz2
  doesn't have a single reference to udev. Convert virtual/udev dependency to
  virtual/libgudev in 0.2.0 using := for automatic rebuild.

*libgaminggear-0.3.0 (08 Jun 2014)

  08 Jun 2014; Sven Vermeulen <swift@gentoo.org> +libgaminggear-0.3.0.ebuild:
  Bump to 0.3.0 (bug #512752) thanks to Dmitry Pisklov

*libgaminggear-0.2.0 (30 May 2014)

  30 May 2014; Sven Vermeulen <swift@gentoo.org> +libgaminggear-0.2.0.ebuild,
  +metadata.xml:
  Adding libgaminggear to the tree, thanks to Dmitry Pisklov (bug #511524)
